<p>The Digital Companion is an elderly robot that is being studied to solve the problems of the elderly in an aging society, such as talking to the elderly and detecting and counteracting emergency situations.</p>

<p>TDRC has established a VR experimental environment to alleviate depression and social isolation in the elderly.</p>
